## Clerk Authentication Integration

For Clerk sign-in and sign-up functionality, **ALWAYS** use shadcn/ui buttons with Clerk modals:

```tsx
// ✅ REQUIRED PATTERN - Clerk with shadcn/ui Button and Modal
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { SignInButton, SignUpButton } from "@clerk/nextjs"

export function AuthButtons() {
  return (
    <>
      <SignInButton mode="modal">
        <Button variant="default">Sign In</Button>
      </SignInButton>
      
      <SignUpButton mode="modal">
        <Button variant="outline">Sign Up</Button>
      </SignUpButton>
    </>
  )
}

// ❌ FORBIDDEN - Custom buttons or non-modal Clerk components
export function AuthButtons() {
  return (
    <>
      <SignInButton>
        <button className="custom-button">Sign In</button> {/* NEVER DO THIS */}
      </SignInButton>
      
      <SignInButton mode="redirect"> {/* NEVER USE REDIRECT MODE */}
        <Button>Sign In</Button>
      </SignInButton>
    </>
  )
}
```

